snippet.title: A Date with Death - Beyond the Bet Trailer
snippet.description:
A Date with Death is a released supernatural romance chat simulator visual novel about the week long bet you enter against the Grim Reaper to attempt to keep your soul. Create your own character, from appearance to pronouns, decorate your apartment, and spend the (possible) last week of your life getting to know the one hunting for your soul.

We're running a Kickstarter RIGHT NOW to fund a brand new DLC: https://kck.st/3wGgvKU

Animation: IMHEL
Music: Hold on to me - Dan Foster
Developers: Two and a Half Studios
